ComicInfo.Summary: The cosmic superhero epic of our time returns for Year Two! COMMANDER ADAM ARCHER and the mysterious NEVER are flung headlong into the psychedelic landscape of a surreal new reality. What they find there will shock and surprise new and old readers alike! Don’t miss this unforgettable turning point in the life of humanity’s emissary to the stars! GØDLAND IS BACK FOR THE ATTACK!
